title: Texans take on Jaguars in Week 6 matchup
text:
Texans take on Jaguars in Week 6 matchup Published On: Oct 18 2015 12:11:14 PM CDT Updated 0 m (Photo by Sam Greenwood/Getty Images) JACKSONVILLE, Fla. - 
The Texans seek to avoid a 1-6 start against the Jacksonville Jaguars on Sunday. 
After being listed as questionable on the Texans' injury report, defensive end J.J. Watt will be active. 
Scoring Summary Texans LB Clowney out with ankle injury 
Fourth quarter 
8:12 -- Texans quarterback Brian Hoyer throws a 26-yard touchdown pass to receiver DeAndre Hopkins -- Houston 24, Jacksonville 14 
11:27 -- Texans quarterback Brian Hoyer throws a 9-yard touchdown pass to receiver DeAndre Hopkins (Nick Novak made PAT) -- Houston -- 17, Jacksonville 14 
Third quarter 
0:05 -- Jaguars quarterback Blake Bortles throws a 29-yard touchdown pass to tight end Julius Thomas (Jason Myers made PAT) -- Jacksonville 14, Houston 10 
Second quarter 
6:42 -- Texans kicker Nick Novak makes 41-yard field goal -- Houston -- 10, Jacksonville 7 
9:44 -- Jaguars quarterback Blake Bortles throws a 2-yard touchdown pass to Allen Robinson (Jason Myers made PAT) -- Houston --7 Jacksonville -- 7 
First quarter 
1:42 -- Texans quarterback Brian Hoyer throws a 14-yard touchdown pass to running back Arian Foster (Nick Novak made PAT) -- Houston -- 7, Jacksonville -- 0 Live Blog Week 6: Houston Texans vs. Jacksonville Jaguars
